textContent:
2 oz or 60 ml Light white rum
1 oz or 30 ml Lime juice
0.5 oz or 15 ml Simple syrup
0.25 oz or 7.5 ml Yellow Chartreuse
0.25 oz Yellow Chartreuse float

Whip shake with a little crushed ice
Open pour into goblet and top with more crushed ice
Top with yellow chartreuse and garnish with mint
